jasima.core.simulation

类 SimEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • jasima.core.simulation.SimEvent
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.lang.Comparable<SimEvent>, java.lang.Runnable
    直接已知子类:
    Simulation.MethodCallEvent

    public abstract class SimEvent
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<SimEvent>, java.lang.Runnable
    Abstract base class for all simulation events. Events are sequenced by an Simulation.EventQueue according to their time, priority and event number (to enforce FIFO order of concurrent events with the same priority).
    作者:
    Torsten Hildebrandt

      • isAppEvent

        public boolean isAppEvent()
        An application event is the usual event type in a simulation. A simulation is terminated if the event queue is empty or does not contain any application events (i.e. isAppEvent() of all events in the queue returns false).
